Title: Signing Complete!
SigningMessage: You have signed the document. The document will be securely stored on the DocuSign, Inc. servers.
SandboxText: Get Started with the DocuSign API Today
Description: With a developer sandbox, you can test our APIs for free. Sandbox accounts do not expire and have enterprise-level features enabled.

SigningCompleteEvent.Name: signing_complete
SigningCompleteEvent.Decription: The recipient has signed the document. The document will be securely stored on the DocuSign, Inc. servers.

DeclineEvent.Name: decline
DeclineEvent.Decription: The recipient declined to sign the document. This has VOIDED the document.

CancelEvent.Name: cancel
CancelEvent.Decription: The recipient has decided to finish later. They clicked 'Finish Later' instead of 'Decline to Sign'.

ExceptionEvent.Name: exception
ExceptionEvent.Decription: An exception has occurred on the server during the signing session. Please check the parameters passed to the web service method.

FaxPendingEvent.Name: fax_pending
FaxPendingEvent.Decription: The recipient has a fax pending.

TtlExpiredEvent.Name: ttl_expired
TtlExpiredEvent.Decription: The token was not used within the timeout period, or the token was already accessed.

ViewingCompleteEvent.Name: viewing_complete
ViewingCompleteEvent.Decription: The recipient did not need to sign, but has completed the viewing ceremony.

SessionTimeoutEvent.Name: session_timeout
SessionTimeoutEvent.Decription: The recipient did not sign the document in time. Timeout is set to 20 minutes.
